# Alpha Platform

Unified investment research platform with two tools:
- **Alpha Terminal** — AI-powered stock analyzer with Scorecard, IC Write-Up, and Live Intelligence tabs
- **Research Hub** — 9-vertical generalist investor reading stack with premium subscription guide

## Deploy to Vercel (3 steps)

1. Push this folder to a GitHub repository
2. Go to vercel.com → Import Project → select the repo
3. Click Deploy (zero config needed — Vercel auto-detects Vite)

## Run locally

```bash
npm install
npm run dev
```
